des:
Crack-up open a cookie to know about your future. Just say Alexa, "open Fortune Cookie" to listen about some interesting future events. If you like the skill please leave a review on the Alexa Skill Store.
Disclaimer- This skill doesn't endorse any of the events listed in the fortune messages. Please take the messages that occur in the fortune cookie in a joke-full manner.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
